2002-12-23 22:41 UTC-0800 Ron Pinkas <ron@ronpinkas.com>
  * include/hbtrace.h
  * source/rtl/trace.c
    Added:
      extern void TraceLogValue( const char * sFile, const char * sTraceMsg, long Value );
      extern void TraceLogPointer( const char * sFile, const char * sTraceMsg, void *Pointer  );

  * include/inet.h
  * source/rtl/inet.c
    + Added HB_INET_CARGO structure
    + Added HB_CRITICAL_INET* Mutex macros.
    + Added auto critical sections protection to all critical sections.
    * Modified InetRecvLine() to:
      InetRecvLine( Socket [,@nResult [, nMax, [, nBufferSize] ] ] ) => cLine

  * source/vm/thread.c
    + Added Stack cleanup in hb_destroyContext().

  * source/rtl/console.c
    * Corrected declaration of hb_consolLock() and hb_consoleUnlock().

  * tests/client.prg
  * tests/server.prg
    * Corrected InetRecvLine() usage.

  * include/ord.ch
    - Removed #define of entries recently added under dbinfo.ch

