2002-12-23 07:38 UTC+0100  Giancarlo Niccolai <giancarlo@niccolai.ws>
  * include/hbapigt.h
  * source/rtl/console.c
    * Chanced the Critical Section for console output into a reentrant
      mutex (manually handed)
    + Added hb_consoleLock() and hb_consoleUnlock() to allow other api part to
      lock the screen
    + Added HB_FUNC HBConsoleLock() and HBConsoleUnlock() to allow PRG to have
      mutex on screen.

  * source/rtl/alert.prg
    ! Fixed MT alert unreadability: adding HBConsoleLock() to Alert, no other
      thread can write
      to screen in the meanwhile

  * tests/client.prg
    ! Check on InetErrorCode has been fixed

