2002-12-13 02:22 UTC-0800 Ron Pinkas <ron@ronpinkas.com>
  * include/regex.h
  * source/rtl/regex.c
    -+ Replaced RegEx engine to PCRE. Written by: Philip Hazel <ph10@cam.ac.uk> Copyright (c) 1997-2001 University of Cambridge.
      This engine is FAR more powerful, and FAR faster.

  * doc/regex.txt
    -+ Replaced with text from pcre.tx which is the complete documentation of PCRE originaly pcre.txt
       /* NOTE: This does include general Regular Expressions documentation, for those intrested. */

  * tests/tstregex.prg
