2002-12-11 03:04 UTC-0800 Ron Pinkas <ron@ronpinkas.com>
  + include/regex.h
  + source/rtl/regex.c
    + Added RegEx engine based on RegEx 4.4-2 Copyright 1992, 1993, 1994, 1997 Henry Spencer.
    + New RegEx Search function HB_AtX( <sRegEx>, <sTring>, <lCaseSensitive>, [[@]nStart], [[@]nEnd] ) => <sFoundText>
      /* if nStart and/or nEnd are passed BY REFERENCE, they will be set to Start and Length of found text. */

  + doc/regex.txt
    + Copyright notice as per COPYRIGHT terms.

  + tests/tstregex.prg
    + Small demo test of new HB_AtX( <sRegEx>, <sTring>, <lCaseSensitive>, [[@]nStart], [[@]nEnd] )

