2002-12-06 09:34 UTC-0800 Ron Pinkas <ron@ronpinkas.com>
  * source/compiler/exproptb.c
  * source/macro/macrob.c
    * Touched to force compilation of expropt2.c

  * include/hbexprb.c
    - Removed code duplicated in expropt2.c (hb_compReduceEQ())

  * source/common/expropt2.c
    + Added #ifdef HB_OPTIMIZE_LOGICAL_COMPARISON guard to optimizations of:
         Exp == .T. -> Exp
         Exp == .F. -> ! Exp
         .T. == Exp -> Exp
         .F. == Exp -> ! Exp
     because of compatibility side effect: IF NIL == .T. -> IF NIL // R/T Error.

2002-12-06 00:01 UTC-0800 Ron Pinkas <ron@ronpinkas.com>
  * source/macro/macro.slx
    ! Fixed gpf related to yylval.string not being reset to NIL

2002-12-06 01:00 UTC-0300 Walter Negro <anegro@overnet.com.ar>
