2002-12-05 17:50 UTC-0300 Walter Negro <anegro@overnet.com.ar>
  * source/rtl/tbrowse.prg
    * now tbrowse support:

    * support nTop,nLeft,nRigth,nBottom increase/decrease dynamically
      with automatic adjustment of the width of the columns.

    + add support for Border with dynamic change.
    * add support for change dynamic in ColorSpec.

    * Automatic adjust of header/footer if there is not place to show one
      line at least.

    + Generate TBROWSE error for incorrect coordinates.

    * Complete support for dynamic add, del, insert and change (set)
      column with automatic adjustment of the width of the columns.

    * Complete support for dynamic change of freeze columns.

    * Change in code for increase of speed, written mostly by Pritpal Bedi

  all these changes were made, tested, criticized and mutually corrected
  by Pritpal Bedi and Walter Negro.

2002-12-04 17:17 UTC-0800 Ron Pinkas <ron@ronpinkas.com>
  * source/rtl/binnum.c
    * Corrected recent optimization of Bin2L() to support strings shorter than 4 bytes long.

